Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:48.21,Tsuki - OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4)}不住的鼓动  让彼此怯怯难言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:52.50,Tsuki - OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4)}那一刹  你我四目相对
