Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.31,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  你毕业之后打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.10,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,遠距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.10,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,异地恋？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.44,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.44,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.41,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,出たよ　謎の自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.41,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,又来了  谜之自信
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.58,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,同じ高校行く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我们上同一所学校
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.45,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.45,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何？　彼氏も茜と同じ学校受けるってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,什么？  男朋友和你考同一所学校？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,あ　お母さんたちには内緒にしててね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,啊  要跟妈妈她们保密啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,やめときなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,一生付き合うわけじゃないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,又不是要交往一辈子
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.16,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,別れたらどうすんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.16,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,要是分手了怎么办？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,責任とれんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,能接受得了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.55,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,気持ちは分かるけどさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.55,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我也明白你的感受
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.07,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,別れないもん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.07,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不会分手的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.93,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.93,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小茜…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,次にまとめの文章を見てみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,接下来看看文章的总结
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,現在進行形だと「am waiting」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,现在进行时是「am waiting」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,過去進行形だと「was waiting」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,过去进行时则是「was waiting」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.65,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.65,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.86,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎　ごはん食べちゃいなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.86,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小太郎  来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.76,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,いらない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.76,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.21,0:08:22.90,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:22.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.88,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,少しは食べておきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.88,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,多少吃一点吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}交際ってマジで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的在交往吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あれってマジなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是真的吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.10,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すっげえじゃん　コタ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.10,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你好厉害  小太
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.14,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,水野さんと同じ学校受けるんだって？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.14,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,听说你要和水野同学考一所高中？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.61,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,噂になってるぞ　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.61,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你的事都传开了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.94,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,マジか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.94,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,不会吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,嘘　マジで？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我去  真的假的？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.96,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,すごくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.96,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,这么厉害？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,全然　そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,没有啦  怎么会
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.43,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ラブラブすぎでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.43,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,太恩爱了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.65,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,結婚しちゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.65,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你们结婚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.18,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,なんかムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.18,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,感觉有些火大
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.25,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,リア充め
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.25,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,死现充
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.38,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,水野さんって　成績いいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.38,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,水野同学  成绩很好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.72,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,そこは愛の力でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.72,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,这里就要靠爱的力量了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.34,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,んな甘くねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.34,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,怎么可能那么简单
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.78,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ギブ…ギブ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.78,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,投降  投降
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.36,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,本気なの？　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.36,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.52,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.52,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.70,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,光明無理じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.70,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,光明没戏的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,偏差値60オーバーだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,偏差值超过60的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.74,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺ならともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.74,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我的话还差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.64,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,俺はコタちゃんの味方だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.64,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我可是小太的伙伴哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.67,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,お前さっきから近いから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.67,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你从刚才开始就靠的太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.12,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,きめーよ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.12,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,你好恶心啊
