Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.58,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,给  安昙
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.32,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.32,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,给
